{"tid":770414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京宅男重鎮秋葉原　竟出現誇張「乳野郎」拉麵店","createTime":"2018-08-07T05:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T07:38:20.000Z","uid":75969,"like":506,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"763ec6d31183e4930038bab6b386d527873b29c2","tid":770414,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本情色文化無極限，現在終於將魔爪伸向拉麵界了，最近網上盛傳在宅男重鎮秋葉原車站附近，有一家「豚野郎」拉麵店，最近居然改名叫「乳野郎」，並有穿著改良傳統工作服的超級爆乳女師傅為客人親自下麵，在日本推特已經大推一系列照片，幾乎所有宅男們都瘋狂詢問細節，正確消息指出，原來這是拉麵店與電玩遊戲結合的限定店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1478756-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1478756-XXL.jpg&h=41bdc86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲位於秋葉原車站附近的「乳野郎拉麵店」。（圖／翻攝日本推特）<br />\n<br />\n這個由電玩遊戲《peach ball》聯名「豚野郎拉麵 」期間限定活動，請到年輕寫真偶像清水藍理（清水あいり），從8月3到5號三天擔任火辣的拉麵師傅親自下廚，同時推出限量「燒牛肉雙蛋黃爆乳無湯拉麵」（爆乳湯切り），曾去嘗試過的日本民眾說：「口感很好吃，燒牛肉也做得很好。 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1478754-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1478754-XXL.jpg&h=ad8656f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「乳野郎拉麵店」的爆乳女師傅，其實是寫真偶像清水藍理。（圖／翻攝日本推特）<br />\n<br />\n不少沒玩過遊戲也直喊「揪團」前往，有網友說「下次去東京出差可以去吃看看。」不過也有去過的網友留言說：「不是天天有姊在阿！」看來能不能遇到爆乳女師傅或美女店員，完全就要憑運氣了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1478769-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1478769-XXL.jpg&h=8ee33bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「豚野郎拉麵 x peach ball 」販售期限只到本月19號為止（圖／翻攝日本推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/08/06/1478772-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F1478772-XXL.jpg&h=22e74659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「乳野郎拉麵店」性感女師傅清水藍理。（圖／翻攝日本推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjzQ0hMVsAA4RF-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjzQ0hMVsAA4RF-.jpg&h=3fa8d440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dj0ASygVAAAe4P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDj0ASygVAAAe4P6.jpg&h=e14b8973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjzQ0hQU0AAUEqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjzQ0hQU0AAUEqJ.jpg&h=965e5695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=412997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D412997&d=gV%2FhBUUaK4F2E3PEbKxKdv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=17e238dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D412997&h=1a9c6b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=412997</a><br />\n<br />\n大奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd9ffcb5da645137c8d79f55c35a26080a01d1d","tid":770414,"uid":41368,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"新系列Av？"},{"pid":"e767daa0c8d375937a13877eea478a1dbcd2c175","tid":770414,"uid":48796,"like":149,"dislike":15,"score":134,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"食同色分開得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cce44f4409744f78029740c34fe56df7d314012","tid":770414,"uid":190928,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc694f53cdede000163af3052e234dd34da68c3","tid":770414,"uid":28181,"like":136,"dislike":15,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201